3 List</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center">December 23, 2023 by <a href="https://lithub.com/author/emily-temple/">Emily Temple</a><div class="post_comment_count"><a href="https://lithub.com/the-ultimate-best-books-of-2023-list/" title="The Ultimate Best Books of 2023 List"><i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i>17</a></div></span></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><div class="article_num">4.</div><a href="https://lithub.com/the-38-best-books-we-read-in-2023/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024books-copy-150x150.jpg" alt="" /></a></div><strong class="title"><a href="https://lithub.com/the-38-best-books-we-read-in-2023/">The 38 Best Books We Read in 2023</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center">December 23, 2023 by <a href="https://lithub.com/author/literary-hub/">Literary Hub</a><div class="post_comment_count"><a href="https://lithub.com/the-38-best-books-we-read-in-2023/" title="The 38 Best Books We Read in 2023"><i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i>11</a></div></span></li></ul></li>
<li id="bm_cross_site_widget-2" class="widget widget_bm_cross_site_widget"><a href="https://bookmarks.reviews"><h2 class="widgettitle"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/bookmarks-logo.png" class="cross-site-logo"></h2>
